---
source: crates/runtime/tests/search/mod.rs
description: "SELECT id, answer, question, subject, trunc(score, 3) as score FROM vector_search(qs, 'second', answer) order by score desc, id LIMIT 4"
---
+---------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
+---------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Sort: score DESC NULLS FIRST, vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).id ASC NULLS LAST, fetch=4                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |   Projection: vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).id, vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).answer, vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).question, vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).subject, trunc(vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).score, Int64(3)) AS score |
|               |     TableScan: vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer) projection=[answer, id, question, score, subject]                                                                                                                                                                                     |
| physical_plan | SortPreservingMergeExec: [score@4 DESC, id@0 ASC NULLS LAST], fetch=4                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |   SortExec: TopK(fetch=4), expr=[score@4 DESC, id@0 ASC NULLS LAST], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |     ProjectionExec: expr=[id@1 as id, answer@0 as answer, question@2 as question, subject@4 as subject, trunc(score@3, 3) as score]                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |       RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |         ProjectionExec: expr=[answer@3 as answer, id@0 as id, question@4 as question, score@2 as score, subject@1 as subject]                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |           HashJoinExec: mode=CollectLeft, join_type=Left, accumulator=MinMaxLeftAccumulator, on=[(id@0, id@1)], projection=[id@0, subject@1, score@2, answer@3, question@5]                                                                                                                    |
|               |             CoalescePartitionsExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |               ProjectionExec: expr=[CAST(key@1 AS Int64) as id, subject@0 as subject, 1 - distance@2 as score]                                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |                 CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |                   RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
|               |                     BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
|               |                       CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |                         S3VectorsQueryExec (INDEX_NAME_1): limit=100                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |             SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |               BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
|               |                 DataSourceExec: partitions=1, partition_sizes=[1]                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
